videos.headline: Henderson bulldozes his way to the end zone for LA Tech
videos.description: Justin Henderson runs over the Florida International defense to score a 29-yard touchdown and give Louisiana Tech a 10-3 lead in the 2nd quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Henderson bulldozes his way to the end zone for LA Tech) 2019/09/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morgan goes deep to Thornton for Panthers' TD
videos.description: James Morgan finds Shemar Thornton with the deep ball for a 31-yard FIU touchdown to give them a 24-20 lead over LA Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Morgan goes deep to Thorton for Panthers' TD) 2019/09/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Henderson scores 6-yard rushing TD for LA Tech
videos.description: Justin Henderson takes the handoff and runs six yards for the touchdown to give LA Tech a 27-24 lead over FIU.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Henderson scores 6-yard rushing TD for LA Tech) 2019/09/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: LA Tech's Smith throws unlikely INT off lineman's foot
videos.description: J'Mar Smith tries to throw the ball to the ground but accidentally throws it off a lineman's foot and ends up in the hands of David Reynolds for a FIU interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (LA Tech's Smith throws unlikely INT off lineman's foot) 2019/09/20 ESHEET
